N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1211.24 - Liquefied argon, helium or nitrogen

State Regulations

Liquefied argon, liquefied helium or liquefied nitrogen
when transported in especially constructed tank vehicles under self
refrigeration with less than 40 p.s.i. absolute pressure are not
restricted. Notes
